Package: metaester
Type: Package
Title: Simulate metatranscriptomics datasets 
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Verónica Lloréns-Rico
Maintainer: Verónica Lloréns-Rico <veronica.llorensrico@kuleuven.vib.be>
Description: This package can be used to simulate metatranscriptomics datasets for mapping and differential expression evaluation with different tools.
    It distributes the total number of reads per sample among the different species simulated, and then among the different genes for each species, and optionally can set
    differentially expressed genes.

License: GNU General Public License v3.0
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true

Imports:
    seqinr (>= 3.4-5),
    pasilla (>= 1.6.0),
    fitdistrplus (>= 1.0-9),
    polyester (>= 1.18.0)
    
Remotes:
    alysafrazee/polyester
